1. Create Page:
	- Open browser 
	- type "localhost/abc/wp-admin" and press enter
		- username: admin
		- password: admin
		- click on "Log In" button
	- click on "Pages" --> All Pages
		- click on "Add New" button
		- create home, about, contact page
			- Title: Home
			- click on "Publish" button
		
			- Title: About
			- click on "Publish" button

			- Title: Contact
			- click on "Publish" button

2. Create Menu:
	- click on "Apperence" --> Menus
	- click on "Create A New Menu" link
		- Menu Name: Header Menu
		- click on "Create Menu" button

3. Add Page in Menu
	- check page (left side)
	- click on "Add to Menus" button

4. Set sequence menu:
	- up and down menu by mouse

5. Menu Settings
	- Automatically add ... (check mark)
	- Main currently set to Top Menu (check mark)




